text: Simone Holtznagel (born 12 July 1993) is an Australian fashion model, best known for her appearance in Australia's Next Top Model (cycle 7). == Australia's Next Top Model == In October 2011, Holtznagel was named as the second runner up in Australia's Next Top Model, Cycle 7 in the finale at the Sydney Opera House. ==Career== Since appearing on Australia's Next Top Model, Holtznagel has featured in campaigns for brands such as Bras N Things, Playboy and Guess.Simone Holtznagel. Chic Management, 28 July 2016. In January 2018, Holtznagel was revealed as a celebrity contestant on the fourth season of the Australian version of I'm a Celebrity...Get Me Out of Here!. In February 2020, she appeared on First Dates. ==References== ==External links== Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:Top Model finalists Category:Australian female models Category:I'm a Celebrity...Get Me Out of Here!
